---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	title_zh="关于"
	description="About this blog and its author."
	description_zh="关于这个博客和它的作者。"
	pubDate={new Date('May 27 2026')}
>
	<div data-i18n-en>
		<p>
			Hi, I'm <strong>seizethe-day</strong>.
		</p>
		<p>
			This blog is called <em>Carpe Diem</em> (Latin for "seize the day"). I write mostly in English,
			with a Chinese translation for each post. Use the toggle in the top-right to switch UI
			language; the post body switches with it.
		</p>
		<p>
			Reach me by <a href="mailto:alice6161616@gmail.com">email</a> or on <a
				href="https://github.com/seizethe-day"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener">GitHub</a
			>.
		</p>
		<p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9em;">
			<em
				>This About page is a placeholder — edit <code>src/pages/about.astro</code> to make it yours.</em
			>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div data-i18n-zh>
		<p>
			你好，我是 <strong>seizethe-day</strong>。
		</p>
		<p>
			这个博客叫 <em>Carpe Diem</em>（拉丁语「抓住今天」）。文章以英文为主，每篇配中文版。右上角可以切换界面和正文的语言。
		</p>
		<p>
			想找我聊：<a href="mailto:alice6161616@gmail.com">alice6161616@gmail.com</a> 或者 <a
				href="https://github.com/seizethe-day"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener">GitHub</a
			>。
		</p>
		<p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9em;">
			<em>这段「关于我」是占位文字，请编辑 <code>src/pages/about.astro</code> 替换成你自己的。</em>
		</p>
	</div>
</Layout>
